WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:07.661
Hey, good morning family. Well, we're going to take communion today. I have some stuff on my heart to talk to you all about.

00:00:07.662 --> 00:00:25.200
He said to me, 'During this great revival that's about to take place, you are about to see something that you've never seen before.'When I was praying into the harvest, he showed me the glory cloud again.

00:00:25.201 --> 00:00:40.959
And he said, 'Brandon, you will see the glory cloud, but it won't happen very often.'He said, 'That's something that I did in the past.'But he said, 'Behold, I'm going to do all things new.

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:52.120
I am going to bring forth new rivers, new oases in the desert.'He said, 'There will be in the days ahead.'Listen to me.

00:00:52.121 --> 00:01:05.353
This will bless you. In the days ahead, a great refreshing is coming to the ones that are dry. A great river is coming.

00:01:05.354 --> 00:01:23.789
And he showed me, he said, 'Brandon, whenever the healing revival and the tent revival started with Jack Coe and Oral Roberts and William Brandon and all them, they would pray for people—and A.A.

00:01:23.790 --> 00:01:33.279
Allen, they would pray for people—and you didn't see anybody falling out like they do now with the courtesy falls. A lot of people fall out.

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:42.719
You see a lot of that stuff and you wonder, 'Is this performance or is it authentic?'I have experienced the authentic.

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:52.490
But whenever we first saw the healing movement of the tent revival, you didn't see anybody falling in those tents. I didn't, at least.

00:01:52.491 --> 00:01:59.700
And when I watch the old revival, I go through and watch the old videos on YouTube that started with Kathryn Kuhlman.

00:01:59.701 --> 00:02:10.615
It looked like—from what I understand, from what I'm trying to pinpoint—and correct me if I'm wrong, any of you elders, if you saw people fall out in tent revivals, then I'm wrong.

00:02:10.616 --> 00:02:21.608
But the Lord showed me that that really started to take off during Kathryn Kuhlman and Benny Hinn and some of the others.

00:02:21.609 --> 00:02:27.359
And now it happens all the time; you see them pray for people, people fall out.

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:39.658
And it was a wave, and then it was the holy laughter and the shaking, and all that happened with Rodney Howard-Browne, and that happened a lot in the '90s. Then it went into the early 2000s and so on, right?

00:02:39.659 --> 00:03:03.518
So the Lord showed me, he said, 'Behold, I'm going to do something new.'And I had an open-eyed vision, and he said, 'Brandon, I saw the glory cloud come in.'But he said, 'What is going to happen with this last outpouring, this last push?'He said, 'I'm going to do something that you've never seen before.

00:03:03.519 --> 00:03:16.347
You need to start to think bigger, for what has been in the past will be something—I'm going to do something new.'And I saw this blonde-headed woman.

00:03:16.348 --> 00:03:21.039
And I saw some other people come down to the front of his meetings.

00:03:21.040 --> 00:03:33.457
And a tangible wind of the spirit of the Lord came in like a mighty rushing wind with cloven tongues of fire like it was in Acts chapter 2.

00:03:33.458 --> 00:03:43.140
And I'm talking—there's no way to explain what I saw; it doesn't make any sense.

00:03:43.141 --> 00:03:59.221
I saw wind blowing these women's hair like a whirlwind, and it was whipping their hair around and their clothes, and they actually could feel the wind of the spirit on them and they fell out that way.

00:03:59.222 --> 00:04:04.331
I saw a wind as you went. It was like the power of the Holy Spirit.

00:04:04.332 --> 00:04:17.279
It was like moving your hand, and I saw the glory moving in the atmosphere, and people could feel the wind of the Holy Spirit in the auditorium.

00:04:17.280 --> 00:04:26.719
And as the wind of the Holy Spirit moved through the auditorium, people were getting healed and their hair was actually tangibly moving.

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:38.959
And the Lord said, 'You've never seen what I'm about to do in these last days.'He said that before, when people would fall out, you had the people in the audience saying, 'Is that real?

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:42.243
Is that real?'with the holy laughter, if they're not experienced.

00:04:42.244 --> 00:04:54.239
But when you feel a tangible move of the Holy Spirit on you—like the glory cloud, everybody could sense it in Azusa Street.

00:04:54.240 --> 00:05:02.583
The glory cloud—they said they played with it as kids; it was a tangible, thick fog.

00:05:02.584 --> 00:05:09.279
And it even talks about it in the Bible; it filled the Holy of Holies.

00:05:09.280 --> 00:05:40.189
But the Lord said to me, 'I'm going to do something new and it will be a refreshing, for my fragrance will fill the atmosphere whenever people are ministering.'He said, 'You will tangibly smell my fragrance, for I carry a fragrance.'And it was a refreshing.

00:05:40.190 --> 00:05:50.102
When people breathe in this fragrance, the Lord said it will be like something you've never smelled—like heaven on earth.

00:05:50.103 --> 00:05:57.373
Breathing in, and you'll be physically healed. It will be a wind of the spirit.

00:05:57.374 --> 00:06:12.719
I saw people being touched by the Shekinah glory in a different way than we've ever seen before. He's going to do something like we've never seen before.

00:06:12.720 --> 00:06:20.079
And I saw the wind whipping around people's hair and it was moving on them and they were being refreshed.

00:06:20.080 --> 00:06:27.038
And old wineskins that had turned into vinegar turned into new wine.

00:06:27.039 --> 00:06:37.304
A new fragrance, a new presence of the Lord will be like an oasis in the days ahead on people in major services.

00:06:37.305 --> 00:06:45.124
And I'm telling you, they're coming from the north; I'm telling you, they're coming from the south; they're coming from the east; they're coming from the west.

00:06:45.125 --> 00:06:54.506
People are hungry and they're desperate for a move of God. They're desperate for a fresh touch from the Lord.

00:06:54.507 --> 00:06:59.220
And I'm telling you, he said, 'My yoke is easy and my burden is light.

00:06:59.221 --> 00:07:07.735
Come unto me all ye that are heavy laden and I will give you rest.'Do you understand what God is about to do?

00:07:07.736 --> 00:07:18.959
We've never seen it in generations past. We're going to see a fresh touch of the fire of the Holy Spirit on every single person who is thirsty.

00:07:18.960 --> 00:07:23.439
Those that are hungry, he said he's going to give you fresh meat.

00:07:23.440 --> 00:07:35.038
Something new and tangible is coming and he's looking for an 'all hands on deck'experience who will just say yes.

00:07:35.039 --> 00:07:48.035
He said he would pour out his spirit upon all flesh. And I believe right now we are at that place where he said, 'Brandon, it's time to become more active in fasting.

00:07:48.036 --> 00:07:55.396
It's time to become more in line with prayer and fasting. Pray and fast.

00:07:55.397 --> 00:08:11.834
Seek me daily and you will find me.'I said, 'Lord, I need a fresh touch.'Give me that living water and let it overflow.

00:08:11.835 --> 00:08:20.187
Not ministering to people out of your reserves, but ministering to my people out of the overflow of your heart.

00:08:20.188 --> 00:08:32.716
Out of the overflow to the extreme, to the full, until it overflows—out of your belly shall flow rivers of living water.

00:08:32.717 --> 00:08:51.893
And he told me, he said, 'That will come through fasting and prayer, seeking me daily, and you will find me.'And out of this personal, more intimate relationship with me will become a greater overflow out of you for the people.

00:08:51.894 --> 00:08:58.879
But you'll not get there until you have intimacy even on a greater level with me.

00:08:58.880 --> 00:09:04.303
There's many of my ministers, he said, that are trying to minister out of their reserves.

00:09:04.304 --> 00:09:13.357
And many of them are ministering in a dry place. But he said, 'I want you to drink from my river.

00:09:13.358 --> 00:09:21.568
Drink from the well that never shall run dry.'Do you understand?

00:09:21.569 --> 00:09:29.328
'Fill my cup, Lord. I lift it up, Lord.'That's where he's at.

00:09:29.329 --> 00:09:40.097
And he told me, he said, 'He's uncapping those wells of revival.'And I told you what I saw about ORU and about what he's going to do with the students there on the ORU campus.

00:09:40.098 --> 00:09:50.024
And he said, 'I'm going to bring forth a great and mighty revival with this young generation, and it will be through the Mabee Center.

00:09:50.025 --> 00:10:02.951
And I'm going to fill that Mabee Center up.'And I'm telling you, it's not going to be a convenient move with people. It's time for my bedtime. We've seen it at our church.

00:10:02.952 --> 00:10:12.994
And people—we had probably five or six families that stayed, and the rest of the congregation left because it got too late for them.

00:10:12.995 --> 00:10:24.319
How desperate are you? How hungry? How thirsty are you? How hungry? How desperate? How thirsty are you?

00:10:24.320 --> 00:10:31.439
Blessed are those that hunger and thirst after righteousness, for they will be filled.

00:10:31.440 --> 00:10:40.159
I tell you this because it's so important that you shake off the old you and get ready for what God is about to do.

00:10:40.160 --> 00:10:48.714
When you experience the true healing flow of the river of the Holy Spirit, there's no time.

00:10:48.715 --> 00:10:54.180
You can be there all night. Give me an alarm code; I'll turn it on.

00:10:54.181 --> 00:11:07.679
Give me a key; I did that for years. I just want to sit at the feet of Jesus. Who cares about anything else?

00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:16.719
There's nothing else in this earth that I want other than to be a Holy Ghost junkie, you know.

00:11:16.720 --> 00:11:27.999
But I don't want to be addicted to a movement and not see people's lives changed.

00:11:28.000 --> 00:11:42.958
If we get a fresh drink—if we get it—we don't want to be Holy Ghost crack addicts and not get changed, letting it change us where we're getting a Holy Ghost high every time we come in there and we're not taking it out and dumping it out on the nations.

00:11:42.959 --> 00:11:51.995
You can either let it change you, or you can be a Holy Ghost crack addict and come from one high to another high to another high and you don't do anything with it.

00:11:51.996 --> 00:12:09.432
He's not touching you so you can just have your Holy Ghost goosebumps, take it home and don't change, and then you come back the next week and you have to be resurrected spiritually because you're spiritually dead again because you didn't take a day-to-day relationship with the Father.

00:12:09.433 --> 00:12:14.818
You only got a Holy Ghost infilling on Sunday, but the rest of the week you lived like hell.

00:12:14.819 --> 00:12:32.129
The Lord wants you to come unto him and be filled and controlled by the Holy Spirit every single day of your life to the overflow.

00:12:32.130 --> 00:12:39.526
He's touching you with the Holy Ghost and fire so that you can take it to the generation that's dying and thirsty.

00:12:39.527 --> 00:12:48.231
They need a fresh touch from Jesus, and he wants to give it to you so you can give it to them.

00:12:48.232 --> 00:12:58.638
Let your life be a light that shines unto all men, women, children, whoever. Let it flow up out of you, out of that river.

00:12:58.639 --> 00:13:07.838
But you look like you have to be raised from the dead when you come on Sunday because you've gone through and you haven't had intimacy with him all week.

00:13:07.839 --> 00:13:11.279
There's something more, and there's something wrong with a lot of it.

00:13:11.280 --> 00:13:21.409
I look at it and say, 'Man, I don't want to be the 25%. I want to be sitting at his feet. I'm desperate for him.

00:13:21.410 --> 00:13:37.199
I need a fresh touch from God.'And what we're about to see, 'If I be lifted up,'he said, 'I will draw all men unto me.'Who cares about popularity?

00:13:37.200 --> 00:13:44.319
Who cares about the finances? I do not care about how much money I'm going to get in the days ahead from investments.

00:13:44.320 --> 00:13:57.637
So what? What is it there for? What did he do it for you for? It wasn't for you to be stupid with it; it's so that you can help further the kingdom.

00:13:57.638 --> 00:14:07.278
Do you understand? He's coming. I've told you a thousand times, and there's so many of you that still don't get it.

00:14:07.279 --> 00:14:13.439
He's coming. Ladies and gentlemen, the King is standing at the door.

00:14:13.440 --> 00:14:21.439
The King is coming. The King is coming. Do you understand? He's coming.

00:14:21.440 --> 00:14:28.246
We're about to see signs in the heavens. We're about to see signs in the earth.

00:14:28.247 --> 00:14:35.679
It's not funny; it's serious. We're about to see some things that are going to shake to awake.

00:14:35.680 --> 00:14:51.518
But are you going to be there with the catcher's mitts ready to receive the people when they're coming in and they're dry and they're thirsty and they're going, 'Man, I need somebody to help me'?

00:14:51.519 --> 00:15:04.119
Are you going to be the one that says come? Are you going to be the one that has the fire to say, 'I know the way. I know you're desperate.

00:15:04.120 --> 00:15:14.559
I know you're hurting, but I know a Jesus that will take care of all that for you if you just bow your knee to him and worship him today'?

00:15:14.560 --> 00:15:27.838
Does that make sense? It's going to take a person that's sold out, that's not worried about a time clock, about convenience.

00:15:27.839 --> 00:15:34.958
A revival, an awakening, is not going to be convenient for a lot of you.

00:15:34.959 --> 00:15:40.285
'Well, I didn't get to watch Friends today'or whatever. I don't know, whatever the latest thing is—probably not that.

00:15:40.286 --> 00:15:57.679
'I didn't get to watch my whatever. I need to go home, and I'd like to have my latte.'I'm talking about sold out. Are you sold out for Jesus today? Are you sold out?

00:15:57.680 --> 00:16:06.737
I have to tell you, it's time to just get to that point where you're just desperate, where there's nothing else that matters.

00:16:06.738 --> 00:16:14.479
I'm just saying I got so excited when I saw what he's about to do.

00:16:14.480 --> 00:16:26.220
When I saw all the people that were so broken and so downcast get a fresh touch from Jesus and see their faces changed by the power of the Holy Spirit.

00:16:26.221 --> 00:16:41.999
When you see that heaviness, and they feel that they're so lost, and then they finally have hope—that's what it's all about, showing them the way for what's about to come.

00:16:42.000 --> 00:16:49.584
Yeah, I've seen some dark things, darker than most, but I'm so focused on him.

00:16:49.585 --> 00:16:55.634
I want to be so precise that I don't miss anything that he has for me.

00:16:55.635 --> 00:17:04.098
I do not want to miss anything, and I will lack no good thing that he has for me.

00:17:04.099 --> 00:17:36.284
I said, 'Man, yes, there's a lot of pressure with leading this, but I will tell you this: there's nothing that can compare to sitting at his feet after you fast and you get in that vein.'And you go, 'What is it that is so easy?'Just denying the flesh, taking up the cross, and following him through inconvenience for hunger, inconvenience for what's convenient.

00:17:36.285 --> 00:17:41.674
I told my wife, we were talking about it, she said, 'Brandon, we're so desperate.

00:17:41.675 --> 00:17:51.038
We're so thirsty. We're so hungry for what he's about to do.'I want to be right in the center of it.

00:17:51.039 --> 00:18:01.599
I want to be on the front row of what he's doing and just sit there and soak it up.

00:18:01.600 --> 00:18:07.914
You know, fill my cup, Lord. I'm excited for what's coming, y'all.

00:18:07.915 --> 00:18:14.964
I have an anticipation for what I saw with the glorious outpouring of what he's about to do.

00:18:14.965 --> 00:18:24.045
A new thing, a new thing is coming. And excitement should be inside of you. Anticipation.

00:18:24.046 --> 00:18:34.228
Expectation will bring the manifestation of what you're believing God for. Expect God to do something big in your life.

00:18:34.229 --> 00:18:43.599
And whenever he does it, get ready to share it with your neighbor and tell everyone around you what God has done.

00:18:43.600 --> 00:18:50.776
He doesn't heal you just to heal you. He doesn't bring finances just so you can hoard it up.

00:18:50.777 --> 00:19:02.159
He does things in your life supernaturally to heal your body, to touch you, so that you can do something to tell people about what he's done.

00:19:02.160 --> 00:19:10.959
Look at the lepers. There was only one that came back to give Jesus thanks and say thank you.

00:19:10.960 --> 00:19:21.119
How many of you, whenever he touches your life for what you've been believing for all this time, will not go and give God the praise for what he's done?

00:19:21.120 --> 00:19:27.519
God, I worship you. Lord, you are good and your mercy endures forever.

00:19:27.520 --> 00:19:36.399
For the Lord, he is good and his mercy endures forever. He is worthy of all our praise.

00:19:36.400 --> 00:19:45.439
He is worthy of all our everything. God, you are so good and we just want to say thank you.

00:19:45.440 --> 00:19:54.639
Don't be the leper that doesn't come back and tell Jesus thank you.

00:19:54.640 --> 00:20:10.426
And don't be a doubting Thomas that—if Jesus was healing the sick today for what I'm seeing coming, would he tell you to leave the room because you have no faith to believe for what's about to take place?

00:20:10.427 --> 00:20:28.297
He'll have to bypass you and say, 'Listen, sister so-and-so, we need you to step outside because your faith is dampening the atmosphere.'Or would he say, 'You can stay because we know you know how to tug along and believe for big like he did at Jairus's house'?

00:20:28.298 --> 00:20:41.604
I refuse to be one that Jesus would have to say, 'Please leave the room.'I just want to be with him and say, 'Well done, thy good and faithful servant, Brandon.'You're doing it.

00:20:41.605 --> 00:21:05.071
You believe me for—I stagger not at the promise of God through unbelief, but am strong in faith, giving glory to God, being fully persuaded that what God has promised he's able also to perform it—that he's given one last call, ladies and gentlemen, for the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen.

00:21:05.072 --> 00:21:07.945
So we pray right now and we're going to lift up our president.

00:21:07.946 --> 00:21:16.313
We're going to lift up these meetings and we're going to give God praise for what he's about to do, ladies and gentlemen, in this earth.

00:21:16.314 --> 00:21:27.405
For it will be like waters covering the sea. It will be a Holy Ghost revival throughout this whole world and then the end will come.

00:21:27.406 --> 00:21:38.079
I'm telling you, a major outpouring. So, Father, I thank you, Lord, for you're going to give drink to the thirsty.

00:21:38.080 --> 00:21:45.945
You're going to give bread to the hungry. Father, I thank you, Lord, for those that are dry and thirsty that we come unto you.

00:21:45.946 --> 00:21:55.359
And we're not going to just do it and have a Holy Ghost shake out, but we're going to get filled and we're going to dump it all over those around us.

00:21:55.360 --> 00:22:01.439
Father, I know you touch those around us so that we can touch the nations for you.

00:22:01.440 --> 00:22:26.202
Father, I thank you, Lord, for a Holy Ghost Woodstock and fire Woodstock, that there will be fields of people throughout the whole United States of America filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost and a mighty rushing wind will fill them with cloven tongues of fire.

00:22:26.203 --> 00:22:42.079
There will be a mighty outpouring of the spirit of the Lord that will be something that we've never seen before, and it will be something that touches the nations in a mighty Holy Ghost Woodstock.

00:22:42.080 --> 00:22:48.368
Father, I thank you, Lord, for touching every single person that is represented here today.

00:22:48.369 --> 00:22:53.119
That you would bring them a fresh fire. You would bring a fresh anointing on their life.

00:22:53.120 --> 00:23:01.729
That Father, from the top of their head to the soles of their feet, they're filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit.

00:23:01.730 --> 00:23:15.128
They're stirred right now that they break off the bondage of despair, depression, and anxiety. And they come up higher with the fire in the name of Jesus.

00:23:15.129 --> 00:23:23.575
They shake off the beggar's cloak, they get excited and they stir themselves up by praying in the spirit and by reading their Bible.

00:23:23.576 --> 00:23:33.038
They get in that living river of water and they get themselves stirred up and they're getting on fire for Jesus.

00:23:33.039 --> 00:23:42.680
For the dry and the thirsty are looking for something that is authentic and real. Will we have it to take to them?

00:23:42.681 --> 00:23:50.079
They don't want dried up, dead, dirty old religion, but they want something that's fresh and new.

00:23:50.080 --> 00:23:56.354
That's why they stay away from the churches and they're leaving the churches by the millions because they're tired of religion.

00:23:56.355 --> 00:24:03.279
They want a relationship. And Father, we call forth a fresh relationship today.

00:24:03.280 --> 00:24:10.798
Father, you said that those that seek me will find me. Those that knock, the door will be open unto them.

00:24:10.799 --> 00:24:17.377
Father, I thank you, Lord, that every single person today on this platform is seeking you and they will find you.

00:24:17.378 --> 00:24:25.437
For the eyes of the Lord are running to and fro throughout the whole earth, looking for a heart who's perfect toward him.

00:24:25.438 --> 00:24:35.476
Let your eyes rest upon me, oh God. Let your eyes not have to wander throughout the whole earth anymore because you found your man.

00:24:35.477 --> 00:24:43.826
You found your woman today. We're hungry, thirsty, and desperate.

00:24:43.827 --> 00:24:51.443
We need a fresh touch. We need a fresh drink. We want to be at the spout where the glory comes out.

00:24:51.444 --> 00:25:12.578
Let us be your vessel that goes throughout all the earth and sets the captives free by the blood of the lamb and by the word of our testimony, telling the people that Jesus Christ is alive and he's risen from the dead and he is seated at the right hand of the Father.

00:25:12.579 --> 00:25:26.558
He is not just some pathetic Jesus that was, but he's alive and he is the I Am that I Am, and he is delivering the people because Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:25:26.559 --> 00:25:34.639
And he's healing the sick today if you believe him for it. He's delivering people today if you believe him for it.

00:25:34.640 --> 00:25:44.254
All you have to do is reach out with simple faith and believe that all things are possible to him who believes.

00:25:44.255 --> 00:25:58.125
How bad do you want change in your life? I'm desperate for a move of God. I am hungry for a mighty move of God.

00:25:58.126 --> 00:26:05.278
Let the wind of his spirit flow on me like he did once before in the past.

00:26:05.279 --> 00:26:13.678
I don't want to live in the past. I don't want what I had back then. I want a fresh touch for today.

00:26:13.679 --> 00:26:23.597
I don't want that new wine that was inside of me becoming vinegar and old. I want a fresh Holy Ghost and fire on my life today.

00:26:23.598 --> 00:26:31.096
Being seated at his feet at that throne saying, 'Jesus, touch me one more time.

00:26:31.097 --> 00:26:43.439
Give me a fresh drink, Lord. I need one more touch.'How desperate are you for a touch from Jesus today?

00:26:43.440 --> 00:27:00.798
I'm passionate about it because I've been at the bottom and think, 'Man, if I could just have somebody give me a fresh drink, help me to get to that river, teach me how to get there.'And I found it.

00:27:00.799 --> 00:27:12.452
I have a relationship with Jesus and he visits me. And I want you to have a relationship with Jesus and he'll visit you.

00:27:12.453 --> 00:27:24.639
For he is no respecter of persons, but he is a respecter of faith and he is a respecter of those that diligently seek him.

00:27:24.640 --> 00:27:31.442
He's not going to—it's like if you're just lazy and just like, 'I don't care,'then that's what you'll get.

00:27:31.443 --> 00:27:39.519
But those that are desperate and those that are thirsty and those that are hungry and you say, 'I'm desperate.

00:27:39.520 --> 00:27:49.218
I'm hungry. I need a fresh touch. I need more of it. I need more of you, Lord.'How much more fire do you need?

00:27:49.219 --> 00:27:58.398
How much more do you need of the Holy Spirit in these last days to say, 'Jesus, I don't want to live like this anymore.

00:27:58.399 --> 00:28:10.842
I'm trying to shake you inside.'How bad do you want change in your life today, ladies and gentlemen? It's at his feet. It's at this communion. And it's not hard.

00:28:10.843 --> 00:28:41.857
He made it so that a little child can come to him, a little 5-year-old girl like my little girl that goes to him and says, 'Father, I just want to know you.'He didn't say, 'Come to him as spiritual adults.'He said, 'Come to him as children.'So I come to him as a child.

00:28:41.858 --> 00:28:50.531
